<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش ج ن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٦٥ - ش ج ن]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تشجَّنَ يتشجَّن، تشجُّنًا، فهو مُتشجِّن<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تشجَّن الرَّجلُ:</span> تحزّن وتألّم <span class="c1">"تشجَّن المحبُّ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تشجَّن الشَّجرُ:</span> التفَّت أغصانُه وتشابكت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>